": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036631_1176513656566068_5083145433805685226_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=aXZR8QX62u0Q7kNvgFUBMbT&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBq7UVubrbISomfxnETPxk4NE7Wt62E93oRmX4FzN2sJw&oe=66E046BF"}, {"file_name": "hamster inc._logo.png", "id": "994291158940421", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75330715_994291162273754_3725985153790783386_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Ypsc1SUwWmwQ7kNvgFnY0j7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB6mPxil11Fm6_XOjTcM1RkeS6u4oB3tStTfpt4I5b4Bg&oe=66E03F5C"}, {"file_name": "\u6d77\u62a51080x360\u5907\u90097+\u624b.png", "id": "824648603043255", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75195902_824648606376588_6298033056542748118_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=N46kQlliE1wQ7kNvgG6H-Yt&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAh36yBrFK100ivkXyQl-Yy960tSehTO25QHdffPCV74w&oe=66E02B8F"}]}, "id": "1382466938967099", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "11.png", "id": "1097797137999292", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570288_1097797141332625_692184632505995617_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ryxc4QMmjkkQ7kNvgEUIOWq&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB5KnYVXWW4vglO9KLtQFmenW-Pl0_gT9CCIJHZ3QE1nA&oe=66E01CF1"}, {"file_name": "2-2560x1440.png", "id": "1631350467404912", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035433_1631350470738245_8852123318308072529_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2RZYiGN1-McQ7kNvgE0UoNC&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB87xIgYlCJabCzgHzDMuhwRn-rKMv00Rl-hlUuiKAipA&oe=66E0327A"}, {"file_name": "5-2560x1440.png", "id": "471726615347621", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569432_471726618680954_3135093783903181704_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=58Rhno3PHWMQ7kNvgEKG_a9&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDcaxJ3T2NvtjkSJfxv_OYpK7kdXreAUvA410ZdgKB4Dg&oe=66E02D62"}, {"file_name": "7-2560x1440.png", "id": "1146548799869781", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035337_1146548803203114_4232071023953588234_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MKhwdwk_ITYQ7kNvgFsJ_4x&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAqC5DoCt7qXcQh4NwH8qYXw2PhIbU8yYigVKd7CWLq2Q&oe=66E013FA"}, {"file_name": "1-2560x1440.png", "id": "999610461677141", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031311_999610465010474_1087177970663193150_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=oJIeo6ZOelYQ7kNvgHvzu11&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBfOvYJtjooojsVQc657zyGUGqjD1wrNY26-a0934DPnA&oe=66E01E2B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "2.png", "id": "427799910014327", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75254872_427799913347660_1009234490175775686_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=G507U_L1CucQ7kNvgFpIRnR&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB_xN1pWrN2VtrUEhZ1Suqs52pnBTPLZUw6nDwdhEXUSQ&oe=66E019CF"}, "display_name": "Hamster Inc.", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to \"Hamster Inc.\"! It's a physics building game that supports \"mixed reality\". In this delightful puzzle game, you'll design, build, and then program machines to overcome challenges!\n\n# Creativity and Logic\n- Based on physical principles and logic, think about how to overcome obstacles and help hamsters improve transportation efficiency.\n{1557136708179895}\n\n# Assembling\n- Design and build a variety of machines with over 60 types of blocks.\n- Over 20 special-function blocks that can be programmed, such as ultrasonic sensors, DC motors, radars and more.\n{327773876776917}\n\n# Graphical programming\n- Super easy! Graphical programming makes your creations \"alive\"!\n{406792278927140}\n\n# Explore 6 unique themes\n- Explore Eastern Forests, Automated factories, Sunshine Coast, Western Gobi, Volcanic Tunnels, and Northern snowfields.\n- As you progress, develop your hamster company and unlock new resources and challenges.\n\n# Enjoy the sandbox mode\n- where you can build and program freely without any limitations on the block amount!\n{971212150879070}\n\n# Mixed Reality\nBring your creations into real world and transform the entire room into a dream paradise: \n- Create custom levels by using real furniture and virtual terrain models, \n- Have your car/drone automatically avoid furniture as it moves around the room,\n- Watch virtual creatures interact with real world: like bison running on tables, floors, or beds!\n{897586709048914}\n\nDiscord: https://discord.gg/NkC8bwQEmK\n", "short_description": "\"Hamster Inc.\" is a physics-based building game that supports \"mixed reality.\"\nIn the game, you can build a variety of interesting inventions such as trebuchets, unmanned trucks, robotic arms, and drones to help the hamsters overcome challenges one after another and continuously develop and expand the logistics territory."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "\u6d77\u62a52560x1440\u5907\u90097-2+logo-\u4e2d\u6587.png", "id": "3772762123041281", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/65229464_3772762126374614_5116127187365598796_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=PF2D99oU3PQQ7kNvgFfiYjd&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBPfDJT3jpWvzAjIocAx1he4wK-s0xYZybA6SdioMU7iw&oe=66E01619"}, {"file_name": "icon2.png", "id": "1090290192036087", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57575357_1090290195369420_677972531973123807_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EVmxneZhr6YQ7kNvgFSjV3Q&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAK2PTDmfoS1tXCgAR00j0l3V7zRRnudOMLa7JG1JeHoA&oe=66E036CD"}, {"file_name": "hamster inc._logo_ch.png", "id": "857711756373822", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/754767